Package: GEOAnalysisPipeline
Type: Package
Title: GEO Data Analysis Pipeline for Microarray and RNA-seq
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("GEO-Analysis-Pipeline", "Team", 
           email = "example@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive Shiny-based pipeline for analyzing Gene Expression 
    Omnibus (GEO) datasets. Supports both microarray and RNA-seq data analysis
    including quality control, normalization, differential expression analysis,
    and report generation. Includes example workflows for cervical cancer research.
    完整的GEO数据分析流程，支持微阵列和RNA-seq数据分析，包含质控、标准化、
    差异表达分析和报告生成。包含宫颈癌研究示例工作流。
